1)Login URL = https://testffc.nimapinfotech.com/auth/login

I set environment and variables and after write this below code in the body and perform POST method.
and Login with valid and Invalid credential.

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

2)Add Customer URL= https://testffc.nimapinfotech.com/customers

I set environment and variables and after write this below code in the body and perform POST method.
and Add customer.

{
    "Customer Name": "Sakshi",
    "Mobile Number": "8669450158",
    "email": "johndoe@example.com"
   
}


